node.text:
These Spicy Sriracha Tofu Rice Bowls (air fryer or oven directions) make a flavorful protein-packed meatless meal that comes together quickly! Tofu is a great blank slate and super versatile since it soaks up the flavors of anything you marinate it in – sort of like the vegetarian’s chicken. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
6B 11G 3P #WW SP 453 Cals 29 Protein 38 Carbs 20 Fats 

Recipe link in profile https://www.skinnytaste.com/sriracha-tofu/ #skinnytaste #wwrecipes #skinnytasterecipe #healthyfood #healthyrecipes #weightwatchers #myww #recipes #healthy #macros #macrofriendly #healthyeats #tofu #vegetarian #vegan #glutenfree #airfryer #airfryerrecipes

node.text: Everyone loves Tommy’s home-fries! And yes, he uses canned diced potatoes which makes them quick and easy (trust me here!) He also likes to use a wok for maximum surface area to get those potatoes really browned. There’s no recipe, just a little olive oil, onion, drained potatoes, salt and adobo seasoning (or any seasoned salt). Enjoy! #breakfast #breakfastpotatoes #potatoes #homefries #glutenfree #yummy

node.text:
Sausage, Pepper and Onion Stromboli (Stuffed Sausage Bread) stuffed with Italian chicken sausage, peppers, onions, pomodoro and mozzarella. SO good!! It's basically a stuffed, rolled pizza. I used @delallofoods pizza kit to make the dough, which I always have stocked in my pantry! We usually make this as an app to serve a crowd but it's also great for lunch or dinner with a green salad!
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
https://www.skinnytaste.com/sausage-pepper-and-onion-stromboli/ #skinnytaste #wwrecipes #skinnytasterecipe #healthyfood #healthyrecipes #weightwatchers #myww #recipes #healthy #macros #macrofriendly #healthyeats #stromboli #sausagebread
